LeBron Is Actually A GENIUS!! #nba #basketball #lebronjames #basketballshorts
description:
Isolations in 5v5 are not about the person in front of
you. You must know the help defense, because that is where your main defender is leading you to. If you read the help, then you will know how to attack the person in front of you and what moves you can actually pull off.
This is also why off ball movement during isolations are key. If Tristan Thompson didn't set a decoy flare screen, LeBron James wouldn't have had a shot that easy at the rim. Rather, Ibaka probably would've stayed down and LeBron would ve had settle for a middy or a heavily contested layup.
